-- Colombia’s Grupo Sura Says ING Purchase Approved By Chile
-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 2011-12-16T20:29:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-16/colombia-s-grupo-sura-says-ing-purchase-approved-by-chile.html
Grupo de Inversiones Suramericana
SA (GRUPOSUR) , parent company of  Colombia ’s biggest bank, said  Chile ’s
securities regulator approved its acquisition of ING Groep NV’s
assets.  The company said in a regulatory filing today that it
expects approvals from Uruguay’s authorities in “coming days.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota at 
